com.adobe.cq.commerce.api.asset

Interface ProductAssetManager


  • @ProviderType
public interface ProductAssetManager
    The ProductAssetManager provides methods to retrieve, update, create and update product assets. A product asset is a resource in the repository and has properties that define its rendering, e.g. the path to the referenced asset, the resource type to render it, a width, a height, ...
